OUTBREAKS ON THE OPRAH WINFREY SHOW, 26 JUNE 1996
=================================================
Date: Tue, 18 Jun 1996 16:05:23 -0500 (CDT)
From: Jim Brady <brady@interaccess.com>
We will be showing a program on deadly disease outbreaks, featuring Laurie
Garrett, author of "The Coming Plague".
Scheduled to air June 26 at the regular time for Oprah.
--
Jim Brady
<brady@interaccess.com>
[This is for information only & does not imply endorsement by ProMED-mail or
FAS.
Laurie Garrett pointed out to me that this is a unique opportunity to get
the story of emerging diseases across to 20 million viewers - Mod.JW]
